Installing PipeWalker


* Unix/Linux and similar systems:
  -------------------------------
  Simply type

    ./configure
    make
    make install

  You need libSDL, libGL and libpng developer
  libraries and header files.


* Microsoft Windows:
  ------------------
  Use PipeWalker.sln solution file to build
  in Visual Studio 2010.
  You need Windows Platform SDK and SDL developer
  libraries and header files to build the solution.

  or

  Use MinGW32 with MSYS:
    export CPPFLAGS="-I/usr/local/include"
    export LDFLAGS="-L/usr/local/lib"
    ./configure --build=i586-mingw32
    make                    
